relevant_findings.abdominal: Tender to deep palpation in the epigastrium, soft, + bowel sounds, no rebound or guarding
relevant_findings.neurological: Alert and oriented to person, place, and time (A&Ox3), appropriate responses
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, normal S1 and S2, no murmurs, rubs or gallops
relevant_findings.lungs: Clear to auscultation, no wheezes, rales or crackles
